    "description": "<p>HAID BIOTECHNOLOGY INDUSTRY (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of China's Guangdong Haid Group Co., Limited. The Company is specializing in the production and sales of premix feed for aquatic, livestock and poultry.<br>\n<br>\n新加坡海大生物科技实体有限公司为中国广东海大集团股份有限公司在新加坡的全资子公司，是一家专注于畜禽、水产饲料预混料生产、销售企业。</p>",
